node.text:
Hey, friend. We are so thrilled to introduce the all-new #EnduraT22Pro, the latest vape in the Endura series. 🔥🔥

The original #EnduraT18 was designed with simplicity in mind; the T22 Pro is similar but adds certain features to improve your vaping experience. 

Wanna try it out? Hands up👋

🛒@InnokinStore global is live now.💨
